  "title": "Class 3 Driver cum Warehouse Assistant #81950",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Logistics</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Class 3 Driver cum Warehouse Assistant</strong></li><li>Working Location: East</li><li>Working Hours: 5.5 days, (Monday – Friday, 9 AM – 6 PM; Saturday, 9 AM – 2 PM)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary + OT + Performances Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent Role</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Check incoming goods for accuracy and damage and store items properly.</li><li>Pick and pack items according to delivery orders and verify orders before dispatch.</li><li>Load (cartons/bags up to 25kg) and deliver cargo; confirm receipt with customers.</li><li>Collect payments upon delivery where required.</li><li>Follow road safety rules and maintain the delivery vehicle.</li><li>Perform other duties as assigned.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>At least GCE O-Level or equivalent.</li><li>Hold a valid Class 3 or Class 4 driving license: able to drive a 14ft lorry.</li><li>Willing to work overtime when required.</li><li>Candidates without experience are welcome to apply; training will be provided.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#81950 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
